Searching for essential items to pack for a backpacking trip in the Amazon rainforest.

Essential items for a backpacking trip in the Amazon rainforest include a waterproof backpack, mosquito net, water purification tablets, lightweight clothing, a first aid kit, a machete, a map and compass, a flashlight, and high-energy snacks.
